description:
I've teamed up with Pause and Beef to take on Ruins Of The MindCrackers #2, a CTM map featuring many of the builds of the MindCrack server. The goal is to find the player heads of the Mindcrack members scattered around the map, and place these on the victory monument.

PauseUnpause: http://www.youtube.com/PauseUnpause
VintageBeef: http://www.youtube.com/user/VintageBeef

Map By: Joelx1000
Map Download: http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/1698016-ctmcollection-ruins-of-the-mindcrackers-1-2-35k-dls-rotm-2-is-released/
